sentences: Axel Christofer Hedfors (born 18 December 1977), better known by his stage name Axwell, is a Swedish DJ, record producer, remixer and owner of Axtone Records.
He is a two-time DJ Awards winner, and in 2013 he was placed 19th on the DJ Magazine Top 100 DJ Poll.
He remains the third-most DJ-supported producer in the world for two consecutive years on 1001Tracklists Top 101 Producers Rankings.
He remains the third-most DJ-supported producer in the world for two consecutive years on 1001Tracklists Top 101 Producers Rankings.
Four years later, the 13-year-old exchanged his drums for a computer so he could create each element of his music independently.
